Paper: hep-th/9803190

Date: 1998-03-23

Title: Variational Principle in the Algebra of Asymptotic Fields

Authors: O.W. Greenberg (University of Maryland, College Park)

Comments: 15 pages, Latex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D58 (1998) 065004

This paper proposes a variational principle for the solutions of quantumfield theories in which the ``trial functions'' are chosen from the algebra ofasymptotic fields, and illustrates this variational principle in simple cases.